letter
Class Letter

java.lang.Object
  letter.Letter
Direct Known Subclasses:
Constant, Variable
public abstract class Letter
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract class which is used to represent constants and variables. Each Letter exists as a doubleton (one instance for each exponent +1 and -1). Instances within the doubleton considers the other to be its inverse. To enforce this, each concrete Letter (Constant and Variable) can only instantiated by using the LetterFactory singleton.
